《'''迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片'''》（{{lang-en|''Lost: Missing Pieces''}}）是[[美国电视|美国]]电视剧《[[迷失|迷失]]》的[[番外|番外]]作品，共有13段，每段长1至4分钟不等，于《迷失》[[迷失_(第三季)|第3]]和[[迷失_(第四季)|第4季]]之间的空档期播出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=index |title=Lost: Missing Pieces |publisher=[[美国广播公司|ABC]] |accessdate=2009-08-19 |archivedate=2009-08-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090819101756/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=index }}</ref>。2007年11月至2008年1月，[[威讯无线|威讯无线]]用户可以在每周一收看短剧，并且节目1周后就会上传到[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]的网站，提供免费-{zh-hans:在线; zh-tw:線上;zh-hk:在線}-观看<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeffrey "Doc" |date=2007-11-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081001200518/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2007/11/lost-mobisodes-.html |archivedate=2008-10-01 |url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com:80/2007/11/lost-mobisodes-.html |title='Lost' "mobisodes" will release as Webisodes Nov. 12 |publisher=''[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]'' |accessdate=2008-10-01 }}</ref>。全部13集“[[手机剧集|手机剧集]]”（也称“[[网络剧集|网络剧集]]”）都是在[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]的[[檀香山|檀香山]]取景，剧组和演员都是电视剧的原班人马，因此所有剧集都属《迷失》系列作品的正式组成部分<ref name="about">{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2007-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090623082622/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=aboutmissingpieces |url=http://abc.go.com:80/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=aboutmissingpieces |title=About Lost: Missing Pieces |accessdate=2009-06-23 |archivedate=2009-06-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2008年发行的《迷失》第4季{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}中收录了全部13集番外短剧作为特色花絮<ref>{{cite web | last = Spurlin | first = Thomas | date = 2008-12-06 | url = http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/35641/lost-the-complete-fourth-season/ | title = Lost - The Complete Fourth Season | work = DVD Talk | accessdate = 2015-10-27 | archivedate = 2015-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150921060216/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/35641/lost-the-complete-fourth-season/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

制作这一系列短剧的计划于2005年11月公布，原订名称为《迷失视频日记》，但由于合约中的多项限制，节目制作数度延迟。《迷失》的编剧和制片人原本打算将手机剧集设计成独立的剧情段落，围绕《迷失》[[虚构世界|虚构世界]]中尚未出场的两个人物展开，还计划由未加入[[美国演员工会|美国演员工会]]的演员来扮演这两个人物。但是，各工会拒绝支持这一项目，经过数月谈判未果后，节目似乎已被美国广播公司搁置。到了2007年6月，又有报导称网络剧集《迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片》将由《迷失》中的演员出演，共计包含13段情节相互独立的短片<ref>{{cite news|last=Strause |first=Jackie |date=2008-01-31 |url=http://blogs.nypost.com/tv/archives/2008/01/lost_missing_pi.html |title='Lost' Finds 'Missing Pieces' |newspaper=''New York Post'' |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archivedate=2009-04-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090428221240/http://blogs.nypost.com/tv/archives/2008/01/lost_missing_pi.html }}</ref>。除1段短片源自之前电视剧的删剪镜头外，另外12段都是新拍的短剧。评论界对《迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片》的反响褒贬不一，剧集于2008年获得1项[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]提名。

== 制作 ==

=== 立意 ===
2005年11月，《[[迷失|迷失]]》[[迷失_(第二季)|第2季]]开播后不久，《[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]》发文称这年12月到2006年1月间会有22集长度约数分钟的手机剧集投入制作<ref>{{cite journal|last=Wallenstein |first=Andrew |date=2005-11-17 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1001523765 |title='Lost' deal hatched for mobile |work=''[[好莱坞报道|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' |archivedate=2008-05-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080506002741/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1001523765 |publisher=Nielsen Business Media }}</ref>。另据{{lang|en|Zap2it}}网站报导，这些短剧之后会收录在第2季的{{lang|en|DVD}}套装中，其中6集是套装的独家内容<ref>{{cite web|work=Zap2it |title='Lost' Goes Mobile with 'Video Diaries' |accessdate=2007-03-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070302030811/http://tv.zap2it.com/tveditorial/tve_main/1%2C1002%2C271%7C98737%7C1%7C%2C00.html |date=2005-11-21 |url=http://tv.zap2it.com/tveditorial/tve_main/1,1002,271%7C98737%7C1%7C,00.html |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2007-03-02 }}</ref>。与电视剧不同的是，这些短剧原计划不由试金石电视（之后的{{lang|en|ABC}}工作室）制作，并且打算找没有加入美国演员工会的演员出演，只不过仍由电视剧的制片人[[戴蒙·林道夫|戴蒙·林道夫]]和卡尔顿·库斯（{{lang|en|Carlton Cuse}}）制作<ref>{{cite web|last=Serpe |first=Gina |date=2005-11-17 |title="Lost" Finds Its Calling |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060527101248/http://www.eonline.com/News/Items/0%2C1%2C17795%2C00.html |archivedate=2006-05-27 |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/51103/lost-finds-its-calling |publisher=E! |accessdate=2015-10-27 }}</ref>。为了解答《迷失》剧迷对30多个背景人物的疑问，《迷失视频日记》将以独立剧集展开，讲述[[海洋航空815号班机空难|海洋航空815号班机空难]]两名幸存者的故事，两人之前都曾在《迷失》中提及，但没有出场<ref>{{cite web|first=Keith |last=McDuffee |date=2005-11-17 |title=Lost Video Diaries, coming to a cellphone near you |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090814050113/http://www.tvsquad.com/2005/11/17/lost-video-diaries-coming-to-a-cellphone-near-you/ |url=http://www.tvsquad.com/2005/11/17/lost-video-diaries-coming-to-a-cellphone-near-you |work=TV Squad |accessdate=2009-08-14 |archivedate=2009-08-14 }}</ref>。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》于2006年1月报导称（短剧原计划在这个月开播）<ref>{{cite news|last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |date=2006-01-23 |archivedate=2010-09-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100912005953/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1001882918 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1001882918 |title=Touchstone offers 'Lost' cast a raise |work=''Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2010-09-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，短剧将通过[[威讯无线|威讯无线]]的{{lang|en|V CAST}}首播，每段长度仅有2分钟<ref>{{cite news|last=Fernandez |first=Maria Elena |date=2006-01-03 |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2006/jan/03/entertainment/et-lost3 |title=ABC's 'Lost' is easy to find, and not just on a TV screen |newspaper=''[[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]]'' |accessdate=2015-10-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100315045643/http://articles.latimes.com/2006/jan/03/entertainment/et-lost3 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2010-03-15 }}</ref>。另据《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》报导，威讯最终向美国广播公司支付40万美元购买这些短剧<ref name="nytimes">{{cite news | last = Manly | first = Lorne | date = 2008-10-01 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2006/10/01/arts/television/01manl.html | title = Running the Really Big Show: ‘Lost’ Inc. | newspaper = ''[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]'' | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080308195750/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/10/01/arts/television/01manl.html | archivedate = 2008-03-08 | accessdate = 2015-10-27}}</ref>。

=== 延期 ===
由于演员、[[美国导演工会|导演]]及[[美国编剧工会|编剧工会]]都不愿支持这部[[番外|番外]]节目，其制作被迫延期。2006年4月，各方经谈判达成一场前所未闻的交易<ref>{{cite web |work=ABC Medianet |date=2006-04-24 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120915043028/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=20060424abc03 |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=20060424abc03 |title=Furthering Its Commitment to Being the Leader in the Digital Media Arena, Disney-ABC Television Group's Touchstone Television Finalizes Agreements to Partner with Guilds on "Lost Video Diaries," Original Mini-Episodes Inspired by the Emmy Award-Winning Series for Mobile Distribution |accessdate=2015-10-27 |archivedate=2012-09-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，确保参与制作的各工会成员可以从中获利<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Screen Actors Guild |date=2006-04-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070503232322/http://www.sag.org/sagWebApp/application%3BJSESSIONID_sagWebApp%3DNONE?origin=page1.jsp&event=bea.portal.framework.internal.refresh&pageid=Hidden&contentUrl=%2FNewsAndAnnouncements%2FannouncementLander.jsp&cp=null&announcementPage=%2FContent%2FPublic%2Fmobisodes.htm |archivedate=2007-05-03 |url=http://www.sag.org/sagWebApp/application;JSESSIONID_sagWebApp=NONE?origin=page1.jsp&event=bea.portal.framework.internal.refresh&pageid=Hidden&contentUrl=/NewsAndAnnouncements/announcementLander.jsp&cp=null&announcementPage=/Content/Public/mobisodes.htm |title=Screen Actors Guild Reaches Groundbreaking Mobile-Content Agreement For ABC’s ''Lost'' |accessdate=2007-05-03 }}</ref>。这份协议促使林道夫和库斯为《迷失视频日记》设计新剧情，将《迷失》的多个主要角色纳入其中，不过并非所有《迷失》的主要演员都有在协议上签字。据之后成为《迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片》[[执行制片人|执行制片人]]的试金石电视制作执行副总裁巴里·乔森（{{lang|en|Barry Jossen}}）所说：“他们似乎以为自己能从这里面捞到数百万美元的好处，但这根本就不可能。”<ref name="nytimes" />另据《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志报导，这部手机剧集会同《迷失》的[[迷失_(第三季)|第3季]]一起制作并播映<ref>{{cite journal|last=Fritz |first=Ben |date=2006-04-24 |url=http://variety.com/2006/digital/markets-festivals/guilds-map-deal-for-lost-1200335126/ |title=Guilds Map Deal for 'Lost' |journal=''[[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]]'' |accessdate=2015-10-27 |archivedate=2009-07-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090704020039/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117941983.html?categoryid=14&cs=1 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。林道夫和库斯在7月的[[圣迭戈国际动漫展|圣迭戈国际动漫展]]上宣布，投入制作的短剧只有13段，并且会在第3季播出到2006年冬季时的间歇期播出，不会有任何一段留至第3季的{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}独家发行<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lindelof |first1=Damon |author1link=戴蒙·林道夫 |last2=Cuse |first2=Carlton |author3link=布赖恩·伯克 |last3=Burk |first3=Bryan |last4=Garcia |first4=Jorge |author5link=金大贤 |last5=Kim |first5=Daniel Dae |date=2006-07-24 |url=http://lostpedia.wikia.com/wiki/Official_Lost_Podcast_transcript/July_31%2C_2006 |deadurl=no |title=Official Lost Podcast transcript/July 31, 2006 |work=Comic-Con International |via=Lostpedia |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017201625/http://lostpedia.wikia.com/wiki/Official_Lost_Podcast_transcript/July_31%2C_2006 |accessdate=2015-10-27 |archivedate=2015-10-17}}</ref>。这次动漫展上还先行展示了《迷失视频日记》中的几个镜头，显示[[休戈·「赫利」·瑞斯|赫利·瑞斯]]（乔治·加西亚饰）寻找一台还可以使用的[[达摩计划|达摩计划]]视频摄录机<ref>{{cite journal |last=Cotton |first=Mike |date=2006-09-04 |url=http://www.wizarduniverse.com/television/lost/001547909.cfm |title=Lost: Season Three Secrets |journal=''Wizard'' |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20061111111140/http://www.wizarduniverse.com/television/lost/001547909.cfm |accessdate=2006-11-11 |archivedate=2006-11-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，其中装有达摩计划的介绍视频<ref name="ugo">{{cite web|last=Lachonis |first=Jon "DocArzt" |date=2007-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110321095057/http://www.ugo.com/ugo/html/article/?id=18038 |archivedate=2011-03-21 |url=http://www.ugo.com/ugo/html/article/?id=18038 |title=Lost Mobisodes Unraveled |publisher=UGO Networks |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2011-03-21 }}</ref>。片段中还有赫利拍下[[凯特·奥斯顿|凯特·奥斯顿]]（[[伊万杰琳·莉莉|伊万杰琳·莉莉]]饰）和[[詹姆斯·「索耶」·福特|詹姆斯·「索耶」·福特]]（乔什·哈洛威饰）的镜头<ref>{{cite web | last = Reha | first = John | date = 2006-07-25 | url = http://www.comicbookresources.com/news/newsitem.cgi?id=7968 | title = CCI Xtra: More Lost Than Found - "Lost" Season 3 Panel | work = Comic Book Resources | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105083952/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&old=1&id=7968 | accessdate = 2012-11-05 | archivedate = 2012-11-05}}</ref>。但到了冬季的间歇期里，这些网络剧集并没有如期推出，电视和美国广播公司官方网站{{lang|en|ABC.com}}播出的是《迷失瞬间》（{{lang|en|''Lost Moments''}}），其中包含的是之后播映电视剧中剪辑片段<ref>{{cite web | last = Carabott | first = Chris | date = 2006-12-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110524161256/http://tv.ign.com/articles/751/751854p1.html | archivedate = 2011-05-24 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/12/20/lost-moments | title = Lost Moments | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | accessdate = 2015-10-27}}</ref>。2007年1月，《向导》杂志发现，美国广播公司这时仍在就演员合同进行谈判，所以除动漫展上的惊鸿一瞥外，手机剧集肯定还没有投入制作<ref>{{cite journal |last=Caylo |first=Mel |date=2007-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20070127151112/http://www.wizarduniverse.com/television/lost/003056387.cfm |url=http://www.wizarduniverse.com/television/lost/003056387.cfm |title=Wizard Exclusive: ‘Lost’ Mobisodes |journal=''Wizard'' |accessdate=2007-01-27 |archivedate=2007-01-27 }}</ref>。到了2月，《迷失》的[[剧本协调员|剧本协调员]]在回答剧迷提问时表示，这部手机剧集很可能由于各方无法达成协议而被无限期搁置<ref>{{cite web | last = Nations | first = Gregg | date = 2007-02-27 | url = http://forum.thefuselage.com/showthread.php?t=70682 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120213163717/http://forum.thefuselage.com/showthread.php?t=70682 | title = Any infomation on the "Lost Video Diaries" | work = The Fuselage | accessdate = 2012-02-13 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-02-13 }}</ref>。

