2007年6月，林道夫和库斯在接受《好莱坞报道》采访时透露了他们对手机剧集的最终计划。预计节目在第3和第4季之间的空档期播映，观众可以从中了解一些感兴趣的信息，这些信息很可能不会在电视剧里出现，平均每集手机剧集的持续时长只有1分半钟<ref>{{cite news |last=Gough |first=Paul J. |date=2007-06-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151027152628/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lost-wont-end-a-blackout-138790 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lost-wont-end-a-blackout-138790 |title='Lost' won't end 'with a blackout' |publisher=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2015-10-27 |archivedate=2015-10-27 }}</ref>。《迷失》第3季制作期间，众编剧试着将之前没有出场过的两名幸存者[[妮基·费尔南德斯|妮基·费尔南德斯]]（[[基拉·桑切斯|基拉·桑切斯]]饰）和男友保罗（[[罗德里格·桑托罗|罗德里格·桑托罗]]饰）重新带入节目，但两人突然出现带来的反响不佳，所以编剧们安排他们在出演7集后双双死去<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Jensen |first1=Jeff |last2=Snierson |first2=Dan |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006153409/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20011203_3%2C00.html |date=2007-02-08 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20011203_3,00.html |title='Lost' and Found |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-10-06 |archivedate=2014-10-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。林道夫和库斯从中吸取教训，决定手机剧集的关注点同样要放在电视剧的主要人物身上<ref>{{cite journal | last = Littleton | first = Cynthia | date = 2007-10-12 | url = http://variety.com/2007/more/news/lost-the-weight-of-the-wait-1117974014/ | title = The Weight of the Wait | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150927130540/http://variety.com/2007/more/news/lost-the-weight-of-the-wait-1117974014/ | publisher = ''Variety'' | accessdate = 2015-10-27 | archivedate = 2015-10-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。编剧制作每集短剧的报酬是800美元，演员每出演一集则可以获得425美元。众演员签订的合同中还约定，如果这些手机剧集之后通过别的方式发行，他们就还可以获得额外收入。<ref name="nytimes" />

=== 发行 ===
据执行制片人[[爱德华·基齐斯|爱德华·基齐斯]]（{{lang|en|Edward Kitsis}}）表示，这部网络剧集的剧本内容“有时是我们想拍但总是未能实现的一组镜头，有时则只是某些会让人感兴趣的东西”<ref>{{cite web|last=Lachonis |first=Jon "DocArzt" |date=2007-12-11 |title=Lost Executive Producers Eddy and Adam Talk Missing Pieces |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208093031/http://tvblog.ugo.com/index.php/tvblog/more/lost_executive_producers_eddy_and_adam_talk_missing_pieces |publisher=UGO Networks |accessdate=2008-12-08 |archivedate=2008-12-08 |url=http://tvblog.ugo.com/index.php/tvblog/more/lost_executive_producers_eddy_and_adam_talk_missing_pieces }}</ref>。第8集《埋藏的秘密》（{{lang|en|''Buried Secrets''}}）重温了[[迷失_(第一季)|第1季]]中[[白善华|白善华]]（[[金仑珍|金仑珍]]饰）和[[麦可·道森_(Lost档案)|麦可·道森]]（哈罗德·佩里诺饰）之间的微妙情感，还有白善华的丈夫[[权真秀|权真秀]]（[[金大贤|金大贤]]饰）同麦可之间的相互嫌恶<ref>{{cite web|last=Lachonis |first=Jon "DocArzt" |date=2008-01-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208093051/http://www.ugo.com/tv/lost/?cur=yunjin-kim |archivedate=2008-12-08 |url=http://www.ugo.com/tv/lost/?cur=yunjin-kim |title=UGO Talks with Yunjin Kim |publisher=UGO Networks |accessdate=2008-12-08 }}</ref>。编剧原本计划在第1季中进一步发掘这些戏剧冲突，但由于剧迷对白善华和权真秀的夫妻关系反响良好，同时扮演麦可和权真秀的两位演员在戏里又有着良好的化学反应，因此编剧最终放弃了这段三角浪漫关系的构想<ref>{{cite web | last = Goldman | first = Eric | date = 2006-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110524161232/http://tv.ign.com/articles/720/720495p1.html | archivedate = 2011-05-24 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/07/23/comic-con-2006-lost-season-3-revelations | title = Comic-Con 2006: Lost Season 3 Revelations | publisher = IGN | accessdate = 2015-10-28}}</ref>。2007年11月，[[路透社|路透社]]报道称手机剧集将在这个月开始播映<ref>{{cite news | last = Tourtellotte | first = Bob | title = "Quarterlife" highlights Web role in writer strike | agency = [[路透社|Reuters]] | accessdate = 2009-12-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091202113241/http://www.reuters.com/article/internetNews/idUSN0421104620071105?feedType=RSS&feedName=internetNews&rpc=22&sp=true | archivedate = 2009-12-02 | deadurl = yes | date = 2007-11-05 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/internetNews/idUSN0421104620071105?feedType=RSS&feedName=internetNews&rpc=22&sp=true}}</ref>。事实也证明了这一报道，首集《手表》（{{lang|en|''The Watch''}}）突然就经[[威讯无线|威讯无线]]亮相。新1集短剧通常在周一推出，再在1周后经美国广播公司网站作为免费网络剧集提供-{zh-hans:在线; zh-tw:線上;zh-hk:在線}-观看。《迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片》一众编剧获得的合同优惠条件让许多电视编剧有了类似诉求，[[2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工]]也因此在手机剧集发行后爆发<ref>{{cite news | last = Wyatt | first = Edward | title = Webisodes of ‘Lost’: Model Deal for Writers? | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/20/arts/television/20digi.html?_r=2&ref=television&oref=slogin& | newspaper = ''The New York Times'' | accessdate = 2015-10-28 | date = 2007-11-20 | archivedate = 2015-06-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150605061923/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/20/arts/television/20digi.html}}</ref>。所有剧集之后收录在2008年下半年发行的第4季{{lang|en|DVD}}和[[蓝光光盘|蓝光光盘]]套装中作为特别花絮<ref>''Lost: The Complete Fourth Season – The Expanded Experience'', 2008, Disney / Buena Vista</ref>。

=== 剧组成员 ===
虽然之前计划由别的公司制作这部手机剧集<ref>{{cite web|last=Benson |first=Jim |date=2008-11-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060206022230/http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/CA6284925.html |deadurl=no |url=http://www.broadcastingcable.com/news/news-articles/lost-verizon-abc-does-deal/108797 |title=''Lost'' Verizon: ABC Does Deal |work=Broadcasting & Cable |publisher=NewBay Media |accessdate=2015-10-28 |archivedate=2006-02-06 }}</ref>，但《迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片》实际上还是由{{lang|en|ABC}}工作室制作。所有短剧均由执行制片人[[傑克·本德|傑克·本德]]导演，编剧则包括执行制片人林道夫和库斯<ref name="crafts">{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2007-12-24 |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=72525 |title=Episode 112 - Arzt & Crafts |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2008-01-07 |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=73578 |title=Episode 111 – Tropical Depression |archivedate=2009-08-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、制作总监[[伊丽莎白·萨诺夫|伊丽莎白·萨诺夫]]（{{lang|en|Elizabeth Sarnoff}}）<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ABC |title=Episode 104 – Room 23 |date=2007-12-17 |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=70368 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 }}</ref>、制片人[[布莱恩·K·沃恩|布莱恩·K·沃恩]]（{{lang|en|Brian K. Vaughan}}）<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2007-12-10 |title=Episode 106 – Operation: Sleeper |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=70051 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 }}</ref>、执行剧情主编[[克里斯蒂娜·M·金|克里斯蒂娜·M·金]]（{{lang|en|Christina M. Kim}}）<ref name="buried">{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2007-12-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=72471 |title=Episode 105 – Buried Secrets |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 }}</ref>，以及执行制片人[[德鲁·高达|德鲁·高达]]（{{lang|en|Drew Goddard}}）、[[爱德华·基齐斯|爱德华·基齐斯]]（{{lang|en|Edward Kitsis}}）和[[亚当·霍罗威茨|亚当·霍罗威茨]]（{{lang|en|Adam Horowitz}}）<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ABC |title=Episode 113 – So It Begins |date=2008-01-28 |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=78371 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 }}</ref><ref name="hurley">{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2007-11-19 |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=56823 |title=Episode 103 – Hurley and Frogurt |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits }}</ref>。短剧的其他剧组成员包括：负责后期制作的执行制片人[[布賴恩·伯克|布賴恩·伯克]]和负责实物制作的执行制片人让·希金斯（{{lang|en|Jean Higgins}}）。此外，第12集短剧《信封》（{{lang|en|''The Envelope''}}）源自第3季开篇剧集的删除镜头，是《迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片》中唯一的非原创短剧<ref>{{cite video | people = Lindelof, Damon & Mitchell, Elizabeth | title = "A Tale of Two Cities" in ''Lost: The Complete Third Season – The Unexplored Experience'' | publisher = Buena Vista Home Entertainment | chapter = Audio commentary, disc 1 | date = 2007-12-11}}</ref>，其执行制片人为杰夫·皮克纳（{{lang|en|Jeff Pinkner}}），《迷失》的另一位执行制片人[[J·J·艾布斯|J·J·艾布斯]]担任编剧<ref name="envelope">{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2008-01-21 |title=Episode 109 – The Envelope |archivedate=2009-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=77766 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-08-04 }}</ref>。

== 演员和剧情 ==

=== 演员和角色 ===
《迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片》中有许多《迷失》的演员出场。自第2季就没有再在电视剧中露面的佩里诺饰演麦可<ref name="deal">{{cite web|publisher=ABC |title=Episode 111 – The Deal |archivedate=2009-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=69062 |accessdate=2009-08-04 |date=2007-12-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = Live Together, Die Alone | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | episode = 24 | season = [[迷失_(第三季)|3]] | airdate = 2007-05-24}}</ref>，[[马修·福克斯|马修·福克斯]]扮演815航班空难幸存者的领袖[[杰克·谢泼德|杰克·谢泼德]]<ref name="king">{{cite web|publisher=ABC |title=Episode 101 – King of the Castle |date=2007-11-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=67638 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 }}</ref>，伊丽莎白·米切尔（{{lang|en|Elizabeth Mitchell}}）诠释杰克的心上人[[茱莉叶·柏克|茱莉叶·柏克]]<ref name="deal" />，加西亚继续出演赫利一角<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2008-01-21 |title=Episode 108 – Jin Has a Temper |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=76612 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 }}</ref>，金仑珍和金大贤饰演白善华及权真秀夫妇<ref name="buried" />，[[迈克尔·爱默生|迈克尔·爱默生]]扮演[[本杰明·莱纳斯|本杰明·莱纳斯]]，他是之前就住在岛上的“[[迷失角色列表|其他人]]”的领袖<ref name="king" />。客串演员[[约翰·特里_(演员)|约翰·特里]]（{{lang|en|John Terry}}）<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2007-11-12 |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=56411 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits |title=Episode 107 – The Watch |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 }}</ref>、[[丹尼尔·洛巴克|丹尼尔·洛巴克]]（{{lang|en|Daniel Roebuck}}）<ref>{{cite web | work = The Roebuck Group | date = 2007-11-30 | url = http://www.danielroebuck.com/updates_2007.htm | title = Lost - Update 11/30/07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120421234556/http://www.danielroebuck.com/updates_2007.htm | accessdate = 2015-10-29 | archivedate = 2012-04-21}}</ref>、[[威廉·麦鲍瑟|威廉·麦鲍瑟]]（{{lang|en|William Mapother}}）<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ABC |date=2008-01-14 |url=http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits#t=0&d=74760 |title=Episode 102 – Jack Meet Ethan |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-08-04 |archivedate=2009-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804014626/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/missingpieces/index?pn=missingpiecescredits }}</ref>和[[朱莉·亚当斯|朱莉·亚当斯]]（{{lang|en|Julie Adams}}）<ref name="envelope" />分别回归出演克里斯蒂安·谢泼德（{{lang|en|Christian Shephard}}）、[[迷失角色列表|莱斯利·阿兹特]]、伊森·罗姆（{{lang|en|Ethan Rom}}）和阿梅利亚（{{lang|en|Amelia}}）。参与短剧演出的[[艾蜜莉·迪瑞文|艾蜜莉·迪瑞文]]在电视剧中只以录像中的人物出现<ref name="crafts" />。空难中幸存的狗文森特（{{lang|en|Vincent}}）也在手机剧集中亮相，同样是由名叫“波诺”（{{lang|en|Pono}}）的狗演出<ref>{{cite news | last = Nichols | first = Katherine | date = 2007-03-25 | url = http://archives.starbulletin.com/2007/03/25/features/story01.html | title = Chewing the Scenery | newspaper = ''Honolulu Star Bulletin'' | accessdate = 2015-10-29 | archivedate = 2015-09-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150906222705/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2007/03/25/features/story01.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。客串演员[[西恩·瓦兰|西恩·瓦兰]]（{{lang|en|Sean Whalen}}）在短剧中首度扮演空难幸存者尼尔·弗洛古特（{{lang|en|Neil "Frogurt"}}）<ref name="hurley" />。《迷失》第2季播出期间，编剧及制片人在2006年4月3日的官方[[播客|播客]]中确认，弗洛古特会在第2季的后期节目中亮相<ref>{{cite video | people = Lindelof, Damon & Cuse, Carlton | date = 2006-04-03 | url = http://www.wasted-love.com/mvcollection/Podcasts/Lostpodcast_13_direct.mp3 | archivedate = 2008-02-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080216072220/http://www.wasted-love.com/mvcollection/Podcasts/Lostpodcast_13_direct.mp3 | title = Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | publisher = ABC | accessdate = 2008-02-16 | deadurl = yes | format = MP3}}</ref>，但他之后只在剧集中被提及过一次<ref>{{cite episode | credits = Maeda, Steven (writer) & Dick, Leonard & Laneuville, Eric (director) | title = S.O.S. | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | episode = 19 | season = 2 | airdate = 2006-04-12}}</ref>，第3季也没有现身，只在《迷失》的播客中多次出现<ref>{{cite video|people=Lindelof, Damon & Cuse, Carlton |date=2006-05-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070307124633/http://www.wasted-love.com/mvcollection/Podcasts/Lostpodcast_18_direct.mp3 |url=http://www.wasted-love.com/mvcollection/Podcasts/Lostpodcast_18_direct.mp3 |title=Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast |publisher=ABC |accessdate=2007-03-07 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2007-03-07 |format=MP3 }}</ref>。林道夫和库斯一再声称弗洛古特会在节目中出场<ref>{{cite video | people = Lindelof, Damon & Cuse, Carlton | format = MP3 | title = ''Lost'' Season 4 Panel | work = Comic-Con International 2007 | date = 2007-07-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210185948/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070802.mp3 | archivedate = 2012-02-10 | deadurl = no | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/Lostpodcast_20070802.mp3 | accessdate = 2015-10-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite video | people = Lindelof, Damon & Cuse, Carlton | date = 2007-09-21 | publisher = ABC | accessdate = 2012-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210185352/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/abc/Lostpodcast_20070921.mp3 | deadurl = yes | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/abc/Lostpodcast_20070921.mp3 | title = Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | format = MP3 | archivedate = 2012-02-10}}</ref>。到了[[迷失_(第五季)|第5季]]时，弗洛古特短暂出场，但很快就被带有火焰的箭射死<ref>{{cite web | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.a