== 反响 ==
第13集短剧《就此开局》（{{lang|en|''So It Begins''}}）曾递交[[美国电视艺术与科学学院|美国电视艺术与科学学院]]，角逐特别类短剧真人娱乐节目奖<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | date = 2008-06-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090326065135/http://www.emmys.tv/ballots/specialclass/specialclass.pdf | format = PDF | url = http://www.emmys.tv/ballots/specialclass/specialclass.pdf | title = 2008 Primetime Emmy Awards Nominating Ballot: Special Class | archivedate = 2009-03-26 | accessdate = 2009-03-26}}</ref>。2007年7月17日，执行制片人戴蒙·林道夫、卡尔顿·库斯和巴里·乔森一起获得提名<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Academy of Television Arts & Sciences |date=2008-07-17 |url=http://www.emmys.tv/awards/2008pte/60thpte_noms.php |title=Complete 2008 Nominations List |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090413013409/http://www.emmys.tv/awards/2008pte/60thpte_noms.php |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-04-13 |archivedate=2009-04-13 }}</ref>，但最终在9月13日[[第60届黄金时段艾美奖|第60届]][[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]的[[创意艺术艾美奖|创意艺术艾美奖]]角逐中不敌[[Syfy|Sci Fi頻道]]的《[[太空堡垒卡拉狄加：利刃之回闪|太空堡垒卡拉狄加：利刃之回闪]]》（{{lang|en|''Battlestar Galactica: Razor Flashbacks''}}）<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | date = 2008-09-13 | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | title = 60th Emmy Awards Nominees and Winners | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908133635/http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominees-winners/2008/outstanding-special-class-short-format-live-action-entertainment-programs | archivedate = 2015-09-08 | url = http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominees-winners/2008/outstanding-special-class-short-format-live-action-entertainment-programs}}</ref>。《[[里士满调度时报|里士满调度时报]]》（{{lang|en|''Richmond Times-Dispatch''}}）的道格拉斯·杜尔丹（{{lang|en|Douglas Durdan}}）认为，《手表》的表现既让人满意，又让人不满，因为他无法确定其内容的重要程度，也无法确知其中是否包括将来《迷失》剧集谜团的线索<ref>{{cite news |last=Durdan |first=Douglas |date=2007-11-16 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20141231205256/http://www.richmond.com/entertainment/article_6b87d4bd-a508-561f-bb3a-827a55f062fa.html |accessdate=2015-10-30 |title=Webcasts an Option for TV Viewers |newspaper=''Richmond Times-Dispatch'' |url=http://www.richmond.com/entertainment/article_6b87d4bd-a508-561f-bb3a-827a55f062fa.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-12-31 }}</ref>。《赫利和弗洛古特历险记》（{{lang|en|''The Adventures of Hurley and Frogurt''}}）播出后，{{lang|en|UGO}}网站的乔恩·拉索尼斯（{{lang|en|Jon Lachonis}}）发文称，这些短剧本来应该要填补《迷失》剧情中出现的空白，但播过这么两集后，剧迷却只会对其情节和电视剧毫不相干而毫到郁闷，不过：“现在就断定这部手机剧集完全是浪费时间未免为时过早，因为《迷失》一向都有扶正之前错误的习性，所以好戏很可能还在后头。”此外，评论中还认为弗洛古特是“《迷失》神秘岛屿上最让人厌烦的家伙。”<ref name="ugo" />又过了4集之后，{{lang|en|UGO}}发文称赞节目表现不俗，是制作精良的佳作<ref>{{cite web | last = Lachonis | first = Jon "DocArzt" | date = 2007-12-13 | url = http://www.ugo.com/tv/losts-michael-emerson-talks-lost-mobisodes-blu-ray-and-season-4 | title = Lost's Michael Emerson Talks Lost Mobisodes, Blu Ray, and Season 4 | publisher = UGO Networks | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100312120733/http://www.ugo.com/tv/losts-michael-emerson-talks-lost-mobisodes-blu-ray-and-season-4 | accessdate = 2010-03-12 | archivedate = 2010-03-12 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。《[[广告时代|广告时代]]》（{{lang|en|''Advertising Age''}}）的拉里·多布罗（{{lang|en|Larry Dobrow}}）对前6集短剧评价甚佳，觉得剧集表现出足够的娱乐性和专业性，整个项目堪称“神来之笔”<ref>{{cite news |last=Dobrow |first=Larry |date=2007-12-21 |url=http://adage.com/article/media/lost-producers-give-dobrow-a-gift-loves/122748/ |title='Lost' Producers Give Dobrow a Gift He Loves |newspaper=Advertising Age |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151030083223/http://adage.com/article/media/lost-producers-give-dobrow-a-gift-loves/122748/ |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2015-10-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《向导》（{{lang|en|''Wizard''}}）杂志的乔什·威格勒（{{lang|en|Josh Wigler}}）认为，《迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片》在节目品质和情节的重要性上参差不齐，部分剧集对《迷失》的神话有推动作用。从娱乐性角度而言，表现最好的也不过就是《高尔夫球场上的权真秀》（{{lang|en|''Jin has a Temper-Tantrum on the Golf Course''}}），权真秀在同麦可的比赛中打出很烂的一杆后仰天长叹。总体而言，这样的内容不是很有必要，而且多少有些歇斯底里的意味。<ref>{{cite web |last=Wigler |first=Josh |date=2008-12-01 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20081205091408/http://www.wizarduniverse.com/120108lostseason4review.html |url=http://www.wizarduniverse.com/120108lostseason4review.html |title=[DVD REVIEW] 'LOST: THE COMPLETE FOURTH SEASON' |work=''Wizard'' |accessdate=2008-12-05 |archivedate=2008-12-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

{{lang|en|[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]}}的里·海因斯（{{lang|en|Ree Hines}}）在点评前7集短剧时指出，“《手表》基本上毫无意义”，《赫利和弗洛古特历险记》的笑料也不好笑，《沉睡者行动》（{{lang|en|''Operation: Sleeper''}}）则是“最没用的一集”<ref name="msn">{{cite web|last=Hines |first=Ree |date=2007-12-21 |url=http://www.today.com/id/22262690 |title=Webisodes Offer Little Oasis for 'Lost' |publisher=MSNBC |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2008-12-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210134727/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/22262690 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在他看来，第3集《城堡之王》（{{lang|en|''King of the Castle''}}）由于本一角面无表情但又令人感到卑劣的表现而总体让人感到满意，《23号房间》（{{lang|en|''Room 23''}}）则是这7集中最具潜力的1集<ref name="msn" />。海恩斯最终认为，这些短剧所填补的空白并不必要，未能形成有凝聚力的独立情节，观众看到的不过是一系列支离破碎的镜头，估计比那些被剪掉的内容好不了多少<ref name="msn" />。

{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}网站的克里斯·卡拉波特（{{lang|en|Chris Carabott}}）对每集都按10分制给出评分，并对大部分短剧作出评价<ref>{{cite web | last = Carabott | first = Chris | url = http://www.ign.com/tv/lost/lost-missing-pieces | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121108141358/http://www.ign.com/tv/lost/lost-missing-pieces | title = Lost: Missing Pieces | publisher = IGN | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archivedate = 2012-11-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。他在节目播出4集后表示，“感觉这些小插曲就像大部分删减掉的镜头——而且是有很好的理由来删减的那些”<ref name="ign">{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2007-12-05 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/12/05/lost-missing-pieces-the-deal-review |title=Harold Perrineau Returns as Michael! |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-10-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144657/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/12/05/lost-missing-pieces-the-deal-review |archivedate=2013-08-14 }}</ref>，但他对每集的评分都很高，最低的也有6.5，《手表》则有7.5分，因为所以他觉得《迷失》中杰克和父亲关系一直都很僵，所以这集体现的不同很能打动人<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144650/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/28/lost-missing-pieces-the-watch-review |date=2007-11-28 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/28/lost-missing-pieces-the-watch-review |title=We Check Out the First of the New Lost Webisodes |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。卡拉波特给予《赫利和弗洛古特历险记》的评分为6.5，觉得这集比较有趣，但莉比的死也着实“悲惨”<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2007-11-28 |title=It Seems Hurley Had Some Competition for Libby |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144645/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/28/lost-missing-pieces-the-adventures-of-hurley-and-frogurt-review |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/28/lost-missing-pieces-the-adventures-of-hurley-and-frogurt-review }}</ref>。《城堡之王》得到8.5分，卡拉波特称赞其剧本创作，还认为其中福克斯和爱默生的精彩表演值得登上电视荧屏<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2007-11-28 |title=Ben, You Sly Devil! |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-10-30 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/28/lost-missing-pieces-the-adventures-of-hurley-and-frogurt-review |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144645/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/28/lost-missing-pieces-the-adventures-of-hurley-and-frogurt-review |archivedate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。他还对迈可在《交易》（{{lang|en|''The Deal''}}）中回归感到高兴，可惜的是这集没有提供任何新鲜或令人兴奋的素材<ref name="ign" />。《沉睡者行动》和《埋藏的秘密》的评分均为7.5<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2007-12-12 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/12/13/lost-missing-pieces-operation-sleeper-review |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144700/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/12/13/lost-missing-pieces-operation-sleeper-review |title=Juliet Comes Clean |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |title=Sun and Michael Share an Intimate Moment |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144715/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/02/lost-missing-pieces-buried-secrets-review |date=2008-01-02 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/02/lost-missing-pieces-buried-secrets-review |deadurl=no |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2013-08-14 }}</ref>，《23号房间》则有8分，卡拉波特称赞“（这）正是我们期待已久的那种新内容，定期观看的观众不会错过这些东西，观众也能通过这些内容对岛上事件的本质有更多了解”<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2007-12-19 |title=Walt's Powers Manifest Themselves Once Again |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/12/20/lost-missing-pieces-room-23-review |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144705/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/12/20/lost-missing-pieces-room-23-review |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《阿兹特和工艺品》（{{lang|en|''Arzt and Crafts''}}）同样得到8分，其“设计巧妙的标题”和恰到好处的幽默赢得赞誉<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2008-01-02 |title=Arzt Questions Jack's Leadership |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144710/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/02/lost-missing-pieces-arzt-crafts-review |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/02/lost-missing-pieces-arzt-crafts-review |publisher=IGN |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-08-14 |accessdate=2015-10-30 }}</ref>。《热带低气压》得到8.5分，卡拉波特这集“虽然毫无意义……但还是很可爱”<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2007-01-09 |title=The Story of Poor Arzt's Last Date |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/09/lost-missing-pieces-tropical-depression-review |publisher=IGN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144720/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/09/lost-missing-pieces-tropical-depression-review |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《杰克，这是伊森；伊森，这是杰克》（{{lang|en|''Jack, Meet Ethan.  Ethan?  Jack''}}）也得到8分，卡拉波特特别称赞其中威廉·麦鲍瑟的演技<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2007-01-16 |title=Ethan Rom Opens Up to Jack |archivedate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144725/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/16/lost-missing-pieces-jack-meet-ethan-ethan-jack-review |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/16/lost-missing-pieces-jack-meet-ethan-ethan-jack-review |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-10-30 }}</ref>。他还觉得《高尔夫球场上的权真秀》非常好笑，是《迷失》最搞笑的瞬间之一，短剧获得的评分为7.5<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2008-01-23 |title=Anger Management 2: Golf Course Boogaloo |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144730/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/24/lost-missing-pieces-jin-has-a-temper-tantrum-on-the-golf-course-review |publisher=IGN |archivedate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2015-10-30 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/24/lost-missing-pieces-jin-has-a-temper-tantrum-on-the-golf-course-review }}</ref>。《信封》的评分为6.5<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2007-01-29 |archivedate=2013-08-14 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/30/lost-missing-pieces-the-envelope-review |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144735/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/30/lost-missing-pieces-the-envelope-review |title=What Could Be in Juliet's Mysterious Envelope? |publisher=IGN |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，《就此开局》的得分最高，达到9分，卡拉波特认为，这集让观众对克里斯蒂安·谢泼德有了全新的认识<ref>{{cite web|last=Carabott |first=Chris |date=2008-02-05 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/02/05/lost-missing-pieces-so-it-begins-review |title=In the Final Webisode, Vincent Makes a Surprising New Friend |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2015-10-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814144740/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/02/05/lost-missing-pieces-so-it-begins-review |archivedate=2013-08-14 }}</ref>。

{{lang|en|[[BuddyTV|BuddyTV]]}}网站的奥斯卡·达尔（{{lang|en|Oscar Dahl}}）同样对每集短剧都作出评价。他认为《手表》在短短几分钟里对人物的描述虽然有趣，但“相对而言一文不值”<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019173933/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-1-the-watch-13611.aspx | date = 2007-11-12 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-1-the-watch-13611.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 1, "The Watch" | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，而《赫利和弗洛古特历险记》的表现则要好过《手表》<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2007-11-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019173943/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-2-the-adventures-13770.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-2-the-adventures-13770.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 2, "The Adventures of Hurley and Frogurt" | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。达尔对《城堡之王》的评价好过前两集，称这集短剧证明福克斯和爱默生的演技非常优异<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2007-11-21 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-3-king-of-the-ca-14025.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 3, "King of the Castle" | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019173949/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-3-king-of-the-ca-14025.aspx | archivedate = 2012-10-19}}</ref>。《交易》所获评价又比《城堡之王》更好<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2007-11-27 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-4-the-deal-14175.aspx | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019173956/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-4-the-deal-14175.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 4, "The Deal" | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 }}</ref>。达尔表示，虽然他一直很喜欢和朱莉叶有关的剧情，但《沉睡者行动》却“几乎没什么意义”<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2007-12-04 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-5-operation-slee-14398.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 5, "Operation: Sleeper" | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019174004/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-5-operation-slee-14398.aspx | publisher = BuddyTV }}</ref>。达尔盛赞《23号房间》是“史上最佳手机剧集”<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017082605/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-6-room-23-14619.aspx | first = Oscar | date = 2007-12-11 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-6-room-23-14619.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 6, "Room 23" | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archivedate = 2015-10-17 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，还觉得《阿兹特和工艺品》因为是林道夫编剧而拥有“至今为止任何手机剧集中最出色的对白”<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2007-12-18 | title = Lost: Mobisode 7, "Arzt and Crafts" | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002033003/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-7-arzt-and-craft-14892.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-7-arzt-and-craft-14892.aspx | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。他认为《热带低气压》“虽说并不完全是多此一举，但其中的新信息却没有什么意义”<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2008-01-02 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-9-tropical-depre-15276.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 9, "Tropical Depression" | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019174021/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-9-tropical-depre-15276.aspx | archivedate = 2012-10-19 }}</ref>。达尔总体上“喜欢”《杰克，这是伊森；伊森，这是杰克》，但他觉得这还不足以进入林道夫最优秀的作品行列<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2008-01-08 | publisher = BuddyTV | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-10-jack-meet-eth-15487.aspx | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019174028/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-10-jack-meet-eth-15487.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 10, "Jack, Meet Ethan.  Ethan?  Jack" | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。他认为《高尔夫球场上的权真秀》算是有趣的小品，但剧中的高尔夫球戏段却存在失实之处<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2008-01-15 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-11-jin-has-a-tem-15686.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 11, "Jin Has a Temper-Tantrum on the Golf Course" | publisher = BuddyTV | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019174035/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-11-jin-has-a-tem-15686.aspx | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 }}</ref>。达尔在评价《信封》时指出，《迷失》中的人物多多少少有过一些欺骗性或是不忠实的行为，但这段以删除镜头组成的短剧仍然很酷<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2008-01-22 | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212084619/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-12-the-envelope-15891.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-12-the-envelope-15891.aspx | title = Lost: Mobisode 12, "The Envelope" | publisher = BuddyTV | archivedate = 2013-12-12 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。看过《就此开局》后，达尔表示“不太肯定自己应该如何来评价”这集，因为他一方面很高兴能看到电视剧开局前发生的事，同时也很喜欢以文森特的视角来制作这么一集手机剧集，但另一方面，把本应已经死亡的克里斯蒂安放到已经非常混乱的开局，会更令人感到迷惑不解<ref>{{cite web |last=Dahl |first=Oscar |date=2008-01-29 |title=Lost: Mobisode 13, "So It Begins" |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090723032710/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-13-so-it-begins-16154.aspx |url=http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-mobisode-13-so-it-begins-16154.aspx |publisher=BuddyTV |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2009-07-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

{{lang|en|[[Zap2it|Zap2it]]}}网站的瑞安·麦吉（{{lang|en|Ryan McGee}}）也对全部13集单独给予评价。他觉得《手表》“鼠头蛇尾”<ref>{{cite web|last=McGee |first=Ryan |date=2007-11-12 |publisher=Tribune Media Services |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416204820/http://blog.zap2it.com/lost/2007/11/lost-missing-pi.html |deadurl=yes |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/lost/2007/11/lost-missing-pi.html |title=Missing Pieces Episode 1: 'The Watch' |work=Zap2it |accessdate=2009-04-16 |archivedate=2009-04-16 }}</ref>，《赫利和弗洛古特历险记》则“略有不足”。不过他对《城堡之王》评价甚佳，称这集证明“简洁就是出众的基础”，短剧虽然只有2分半钟长，但却紧张激烈，且包含丰富的信息量，令他自始至终都像[[蜘蛛侠|蜘蛛侠]]般对迷失的神话保持高度敏感<ref>{{cite web |last=McGee |first=Ryan |date=2007-11-26 |url=http://zap2it.com/2007/11/missing-pieces-episode-3-King-of-the-castle/ |title=Missing Pieces Episode 3: King of the Castle |work=Zap2it |publisher=Tribune Media Services |accessdate=2015-10-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151030154246/http://zap2it.com/2007/11/missing-pieces-episode-3-King-of-the-castle/ |11= |archivedate=2015-10-30 }}</ref>。《交易》所获评价不及前几集<ref>{{cite web|last=McGee |url=http://zap2it.com/2007/12/missing-pieces-episode-4-the-deal/ |first=Ryan |work=Zap2it |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416204825/http://blog.zap2it.com/lost/2007/12/missing-pieces.html |deadurl=no |date=2007-12-03 |title=Missing Pieces Episode 4: The Deal |publisher=Tribune Media Services |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2009-04-16 }}</ref>，《23号房间》则“短小精悍”<ref>{{cite web|last=McGee |first=Ryan |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081015060812/http://blog.zap2it.com/lost/2007/12/missing-piece-2.html |date=2007-12-17 |url=http://zap2it.com/2007/12/missing-pieces-episode-6-room-23/ |title=Missing Pieces Episode 6: Room 23 |work=Zap2it |publisher=Tribune Media Services |accessdate=2015-10-30 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2008-10-15 }}</ref>。麦吉觉得《阿兹特和工艺品》的表现相对薄弱，称“遗憾的是，并非任何《迷失》中的内容都可以借达摩计划点石成金”<ref>{{cite web|last=McGee |first=Ryan |date=2007-12-27 |archivedate=2009-04-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416204400/http://blog.zap2it.com/lost/2007/12/missing-piece-3.html |work=Zap2it |publisher=Tribune Media Services |url=http://zap2it.com/2007/12/missing-pieces-episode-7-arzt-and-crafts/ |title=Missing Pieces Episode 7: Arzt and Crafts |accessdate=2015-10-30 }}</ref>。他觉得《埋藏的秘密》表现平庸<ref name="ethan">{{cite web |last=McGee |first=Ryan |date=2008-01-07 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151030160012/http://zap2it.com/2008/01/missing-pieces-episode-10-jack-meet-ethan-ethan-jack/ |url=http://zap2it.com/2008/01/missing-pieces-episode-10-jack-meet-ethan-ethan-jack/ |deadurl=no |title=Missing Pieces Episode 10: Jack, Meet Ethan. Ethan? Jack |work=Zap2it |publisher=Tribune Media Services |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2015-10-30 }}</ref>，对《热带低气压》的评价也不佳，觉得后一集短剧的品质太差，几乎同《迷失》第3季第9集《[[奇人奇地|奇人奇地]]》（{{lang|en|''Stranger in a Strange Land''}}）以及剧中人物[[妮基·费尔南德斯|保罗]]的表现在同一水准<ref>{{cite web|last=McGee |first=Ryan |work=Zap2it |publisher=Tribune Media Services |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416204837/http://blog.zap2it.com/lost/2008/01/piece-ing-it-to.html |deadurl=no |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archivedate=2009-04-16 |date=2008-01-07 |url=http://zap2it.com/2008/01/piece-ing-it-together/ |title=Piece-ing It Together }}</ref>，剧迷及评论界对该人物及这集电视剧的评价都很差<ref>{{cite news | last = Ryan | first = Maureen | newspaper = ''[[芝加哥论坛报|Chicago Tribune]]'' | accessdate = 2015-10-30 | date = 2008-01-29 | deadurl = no | url = http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/01/lost-shockers-a.html | archivedate = 2015-07-15 | title = 'Lost'<nowiki>'</nowiki>s Fab Start to Season 4, and a Chat with Co-Creator Damon Lindelof | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150715214224/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/01/lost-shockers-a.html}}</ref>。在麦吉看来，《杰克，这是伊森；伊森，这是杰克》是整部手机剧集品质回归之作，但剧名实在显得“哆嗦”<ref name="ethan" />。看过《就此开局》后，麦吉称《迷失特辑：遗忘的碎片》总体上是部至关重要的手机剧集，但美国广播公司居然不打算在第4季开播前播映，这实在令人难以置信<ref>{{cite web|last=McGee |first=Ryan |date=2008-01-28 |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/lost/2008/01/i-will-confess.html |title=We've Got Work to Do |archivedate=2009-04-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416204831/http://blog.zap2it.com/lost/2008/01/i-will-confess.html |work=Zap2it |accessdate=2009-04-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

